Notes: Used to help navigate between locations
Place elevators. Rotate them by selecting once placed
Displayed Text: Umistete vytahy. Po umisteni je vyberem otocte

Notes: Place stairs. Rotate them by selecting once placed
Displayed Text: Umisteni schodu. Po umisteni je vyberem otocte.

Notes: Rotate a node to face a different direction
Force the current room to be something in particular
Displayed Text: Vynutit, aby se aktualni mistnost stala necim konkretnim

Notes: Move the map view down a floor.
Displayed Text: Presunuti zobrazeni mapy o patro nize.

Notes: Move the map view up a floor.
Displayed Text: Presunte zobrazeni mapy o patro vys.

Notes: Open a folder containing information on your current location.
Displayed Text: Otevrete slozku obsahujici informace o vasi aktualni poloze.

Notes: Center the map on your current position.
Toggle the direction arrow you see in first person, showing you where to go. You can always press and hold tab to view the map when not in this screen.
Displayed Text: Prepnete smerovou sipku, kterou vidite v prvni osobe a ktera vam ukazuje, kam mate jit. Kdyz nejste na teto obrazovce, muzete vzdy stisknout a podrzet kartu a zobrazit mapu.

Notes: Pin/unpin this evidence item to/from the case board.
Displayed Text: Pripnete/odpojte tento dukazni prostredek k desce kufriku.

Notes: Open a folder containing information on your apartment.
Displayed Text: Otevrete slozku s informacemi o svem byte.

Notes: Create a sticky note to add to the case board. You can write whatever you want on it.
Displayed Text: Vytvorte samolepici poznamku, kterou pridate na nastenku pripadu. Muzete na nej napsat, co chcete.

Notes: Sync disks are DNA based upgrades you can acquire and equip to gain extra ability.
Displayed Text: Sync disky jsou vylepseni zalozena na DNA, ktera muzete ziskat a vybavit, abyste ziskali dalsi schopnosti.

Notes: Locate this location on the map...
Plot a route to this location...
Deselect case to go off duty
Displayed Text: Zruseni vyberu pripadu pro prechod mimo sluzbu

Notes: Create a new sticky note for writing your own notes.
Displayed Text: Vytvorte si novou samolepici poznamku pro psani vlastnich poznamek.

Notes: Create a new case where you can pin information of your choosing.
Displayed Text: Vytvorte novy pripad, do ktereho muzete pripnout informace podle vlastniho vyberu.

Notes: Close this case and remove from the case bar.
Displayed Text: Zavrete tento kufrik a vyjmete jej z listy kufriku.

Notes: Minimize or restore this on the case board.
Displayed Text: Minimalizujte nebo obnovte tuto funkci na desce skrine.

Notes: Create a new custom connection linking to this.
Displayed Text: Vytvorte nove vlastni pripojeni, ktere na nej bude odkazovat.

Notes: Hide or show this connection with string.
Displayed Text: Skryt nebo zobrazit toto pripojeni pomoci retezce.

Notes: Collect a hand-in form for this case to see the questions you need to answer to solve it.
Displayed Text: Vyzvednete si formular pro tento pripad a zjistete, na jake otazky musite odpovedet, abyste ho vyresili.

Notes: Answer these questions to resolve this case.
Displayed Text: Odpovezte na tyto otazky a vyreste tento pripad.

Notes: This increases as you gain more experience. Reaching the maximum level will allow retirement.
Displayed Text: S pribyvajicimi zkusenostmi se tato hodnota zvysuje. Dosazeni maximalni urovne umozni odchod do duchodu.

Notes: Contains useful help, search, quick references and previously-opened folders.
Displayed Text: Obsahuje uzitecnou napovedu, vyhledavani, rychle odkazy a drive otevrene slozky.

Notes: Consumable resource that is used to pick locks or sabotage security equipment.
Displayed Text: Spotrebni zdroj, ktery se pouziva k odemykani zamku nebo sabotazi bezpecnostnich zarizeni.

Notes: Shows your inventory and current statuses.
Point to this location on the map...
Displayed Text: Ukazte na toto misto na mape...

Notes: Plot a route to this location that uses a marked path on the map, and the directional arrow.
Displayed Text: Vyznacte trasu k tomuto mistu pomoci vyznacene cesty na mape a smerove sipky.
Skenovani teto polozky na otisky prstu

Notes: Bring up this item's evidence folder

Notes: Edit the decor of your apartment

If this icon is present it means you are interacting with this item directly (in-world), as opposed to from memory (pinned on case board). More actions may be available to you while interacting with it directly.
Displayed Text: Pokud je tato ikona pritomna, znamena to, ze s danym predmetem pracujete primo (ve svete), a nikoli z pameti (pripnuty na desce kufriku). Pri prime interakci s nim muze byt k dispozici vice akci.

Notes: Toggle between hand-written and clear text display.
Displayed Text: Prepinani mezi rucne psanym a citelnym textem.
